fields.calculatedFormula:
CASE( Charge_Unit__c,
"USD/M2",  m2__c ,
"USD/M3",  m3__c  ,
"USD/PC",  Quantity_Pcs__c  ,
"USD/TON",  Tons__c  ,
"USD/ML",  ml__c  ,
0
)
fields.label: Quantity (For print)
fields.name: Quantity_For_print__c

fields.calculatedFormula:
IF (
    ISBLANK (  Planned_Shipment_Product__c ),
    m3__c *  Product__r.Bottom_cladding_coefficient__c  *  Product__r.specific_gravity__c,
    IF (
        AND (NOT(ISBLANK (  Planned_Shipment_Product__c )), ISBLANK (   Order_Product_C__c  ) ),
        m3__c *  Planned_Shipment_Product__r.Product__r.Bottom_cladding_coefficient__c  * Planned_Shipment_Product__r.Product__r.specific_gravity__c,
        m3__c *  Planned_Shipment_Product__r.Order_Product_C__r.Contract_Product__r.Product__r.Bottom_cladding_coefficient__c  * Planned_Shipment_Product__r.Order_Product_C__r.Contract_Product__r.Product__r.specific_gravity__c
    )
)
fields.label: Tons
fields.name: Tons__c

fields.calculatedFormula:
CASE( Charge_Unit__c,
"USD/M2",  ROUND(Sales_Price_USD__c * ROUND(m2__c,2),2)  ,
"USD/M3", ROUND(Sales_Price_USD__c * ROUND(m3__c,2),2) ,
"USD/PC", ROUND(Sales_Price_USD__c * Quantity_Pcs__c,2) ,
"USD/TON", ROUND(Sales_Price_USD__c * ROUND(Tons__c,2),2) ,
"USD/ML", ROUND(Sales_Price_USD__c * ROUND(ml__c,2),2) ,
0
)
fields.label: Total Price (USD)
fields.name: Total_Price_USD__c

fields.calculatedFormula: IF( CONTAINS( Vietnamese_Description__c , "Đá cột"), Height__c * Quantity_Pcs__c / 100, Length__c * Quantity_Pcs__c / 100)
fields.label: ml
fields.name: ml__c
